name: EKRecurrenceEnd
desc: A class that defines the end of a recurrence rule.

items.name: init(end: Date)
items.desc: Initializes and returns a date-based recurrence end with a given end date.

items.name: init(occurrenceCount: Int)
items.desc: Initializes and returns a count-based recurrence end with a given maximum occurrence count.

items.name: var endDate: Date?
items.desc: The end date of the recurrence end, or nil if the recurrence end is count-based.

items.name: var occurrenceCount: Int
items.desc: The occurrence count of the recurrence end, or 0 if the recurrence end is date-based.
